### CSRF Protection

**Django CSRF Token**:
```javascript
function getCsrfToken() {
  return document.querySelector('[name=csrfmiddlewaretoken]').value;
  // Or from cookies:
  // return getCookie('csrftoken');
}
```

**All POST requests must include**:
```javascript
headers: {
  'X-CSRFToken': getCsrfToken()
}
```

