## Animation System

### Overview
The application uses CSS transitions and animations for smooth, professional interactions.

### Animation Categories

#### 1. Page Entry Animations (AOS - Animate On Scroll)

**Library**: AOS (Animate On Scroll)

**Implementation**:
```html
<div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="600">
  <!-- Content animates up when scrolling into view -->
</div>

<div data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="500">
  <!-- Content fades in from left -->
</div>
```

**Initialization**:
```javascript
AOS.init({
  duration: 600,
  easing: 'ease-in-out',
  once: true  // Animate only once
});
```

**Common Effects**:
- `fade-up`: Element fades in while moving up
- `fade-left`/`fade-right`: Horizontal fade
- `zoom-in`: Element scales up
- `slide-up`: Faster upward movement

